{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/TIL_2019_08_25","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"TIL #1 - Gatsby Link & activeClassName","date":"2019-08-26","tags":["Gatsby","React","TIL"]},"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.6731936557666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Shelf of books\"\n        title=\"Shelf of books\"\n        src=\"/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/48a11/books.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/3dff4/books.jpg 125w,\n/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/9fb78/books.jpg 250w,\n/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/48a11/books.jpg 500w,\n/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/a66cd/books.jpg 750w,\n/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/971c4/books.jpg 1000w,\n/static/4ecbeb4609ba9b631c41f971f3059ad3/cfb5d/books.jpg 5107w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Gatsby Link and activeClassName</h2>\n<p>I've used the Link component from Gatsby before, but didn't know about activeClassName. For those who aren't familiar, Gatsby's Link component is used to create internal links in your Gatsby site. (If you need to link to an external source, just stick with an <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a&gt;</code> tag.)</p>\n<p>In this instance, I'm using it to navigate from the homepage to the Contact page of my website.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Link to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/contact/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Contact<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Link<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>If I add a couple more links inside of an unordered list, I get a navigation menu:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ul<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Link to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/contact/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Contact<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Link<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Link to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/about/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>About<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Link<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Link to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Home<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Link<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>li<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ul<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>The icing on the cake is adding a couple of classnames to each <code class=\"language-text\">Link</code> and a small amount of css.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Link className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"link\"</span> activeClassName<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"active-link\"</span> to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/contact/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Contact<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Link<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.link</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.active-link</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ba2d65<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>With those two bits of additional code, our Contact link will now be pink when the current URL matches the Link's <code class=\"language-text\">to</code> prop <em>exactly</em>. We now have a simple navigation menu.</p>\n<p>Photo by Jessica Ruscello on Unsplash</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"TIL_2019_08_25"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1576482507","1749249851","3010532460","4202924991"]}